      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, devoid of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks, and the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new car. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking perfection.",
