    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including an engine that runs roughly and a transmission that slips, making it unreliable for daily use without major repairs. The exterior has noticeable body damage, including several large dents and significant rust patches on the rocker panels. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be best suited as a donor car for parts or a complete restoration project for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
      "price": 5500.0,
